{
  "id": "6090ec0ba287e6002291a256",
  "title": "Hatena2012-07-31",
  "created": 1343660400,
  "updated": 1343660400,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcab6",
      "text": "Hatena2012-07-31",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcab7",
      "text": "code:hatena",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcab8",
      "text": " <body>",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcab9",
      "text": " *1343701166*Macのスクリーンショットのファイル名を変更",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcaba",
      "text": " デフォルトだと\"スクリーンショット 2012-07-02 15.50.51.png\"とかになってしまって、日本語で始まるからコンソールから扱うのがめんどくさい。defaultsコマンドでプレフィックスを変えることが出来るようだ。",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcabb",
      "text": " >||",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcabc",
      "text": " $ defaults write com.apple.screencapture name \"SS\"",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcabd",
      "text": " $ killall SystemUIServer",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcabe",
      "text": " ||<",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcabf",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcac0",
      "text": " これで\"SS 2012-07-02 15.50.51.png\"という名前で保存されるようになった。本当を言うと空白文字が入っているのも気に入らないので変えたいのだけどもやりかたがわからなかった。",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcac1",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcac2",
      "text": " OSは10.7.4、参考文献 http://usingmac.com/2009/10/19/tweak-screencapture-behavior",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcac3",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcac4",
      "text": " *1343745529*Macのスクリーンショットで1日の作業を記録して動画で振り返り",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcac5",
      "text": " スクリーンショットを10秒に1回撮影して連番の画像で保存するスクリプトを走らせて1日の作業を記録し、一日の最後にffmpegで動画にして振り返りをしてみた。結構面白いよ。",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcac6",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcac7",
      "text": " 社内掲示板やメーラやエディタで文章がにょきにょき伸びていくのが見えるのも楽しいけど、一日の終わりに「ああそうそう、これを調べてたんだった、途中でインタラプトが入って忘れてた」「この調べ物をした後サイドバーに出てた記事を読みふけってしまったけど、必要ではなかったな」「この作業は今やるべきことじゃなかったな」「時間を結構無駄にしたな」などという振り返りができる。反省。",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcac8",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcac9",
      "text": " 10秒に1回撮影したのを10FPSで動画にしているから1時間が36秒になる。もうちょっと速くしてもいいかも。1分に1枚にすると1時間が6秒か。その間くらいかなー。",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcaca",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcacb",
      "text": " 記録用スクリプトが連番で画像を吐いているのは後でffmpegで読み込ませるため。screencaptureはMacの画面撮影コマンド。ffmpegに-s 720x450を指定しているのは、僕の環境の画面が1440x900だからその半分。今回の実験では3500枚くらいのスクリーンショットが撮られて、12MBくらいの動画ができた。",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcacc",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcacd",
      "text": " 記録用スクリプト(python)",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcace",
      "text": " >|python|",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcacf",
      "text": " from time import sleep",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcad0",
      "text": " import subprocess",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcad1",
      "text": " import os",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcad2",
      "text": " outdir = 'screencapture'",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcad3",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcad4",
      "text": " counter = 1",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcad5",
      "text": " def capture():",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcad6",
      "text": "     global counter",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcad7",
      "text": "     filename = '%08d.png' % counter",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcad8",
      "text": "     outpath = os.path.join(outdir, filename)",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcad9",
      "text": "     subprocess.call(['screencapture', outpath])",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcada",
      "text": "     counter += 1",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcadb",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcadc",
      "text": " while True:",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcadd",
      "text": "     capture()",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcade",
      "text": "     sleep(10)",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcadf",
      "text": " ||<",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcae0",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcae1",
      "text": " 動画作成用スクリプト",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcae2",
      "text": " >|sh|",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcae3",
      "text": " #!/bin/bash",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcae4",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcae5",
      "text": " original_images=screencapture",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcae6",
      "text": " ldate=$(date +%Y%m%d)",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcae7",
      "text": " ffmpeg -y -f image2 -r 10 -i \"$original_images/%08d.png\" -s 720x450 \"screencapture$ldate.avi\"",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcae8",
      "text": " ||<",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcae9",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcaea",
      "text": " 追記：複数モニタがある場合は複数ファイル名を指定するといいらしい。",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcaeb",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcaec",
      "text": " 追記：「スクリーンショットをとっておくやつに、isight でとった画像をくっつけて動画にしたらおもしろいとおもうんだけど誰かやらないかな。」by id:tokuhirom 　それはたしかに面白そう。ライフログカメラで作業中の自分の顔を録画したことがあるけど、悩んだり眉毛をいじったり腕を組んだりしていて結構面白い。",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcaed",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcaee",
      "text": " 追記： オプションに-xをつけるとシャッター音を消せる。-Cをつけるとカーソルも撮れるようだ",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcaef",
      "text": " </body>",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2eaff09e00003dcaf0",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1343660400,
      "updated": 1343660400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
